{"tid":473331,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"除左窮人，有錢都唔好生仔","createTime":"2017-11-19T06:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T16:21:29.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"818fa708227af8ecd5811b8fcaf63e2f42377196","tid":473331,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"有錢都辛苦<br />\n只不過冇窮人咁辛苦<br />\n做人就係苦<br />\n錢可以消災解困<br />\n但唔係萬能<br />\n好簡單<br />\n生cancer可以請最好醫生<br />\n但未必醫得返好你<br />\n總之做人就係辛苦<br />\n如果我當初冇來過世上<br />\n其實我冇損失<br />\n冇苦既存在<br />\n但從你有氣息開始<br />\n出世個刻<br />\n就要捱<br />\n有錢人都要捱<br />\n李嘉誠、bill gates、畢菲特、elon musk都要捱<br />\n自己捱埋呢幾廿年就算<br />\n但真係唔好再結婚生仔<br />\n中國人兩句說話<br />\n己所不欲，勿施於人<br />\n早知今日，何必當初<br />\n細佬贈多各位阿姐阿哥一句<br />\n沒料到我所失的竟已是我的所有"},{"pid":"53986089e6d72d3140ed7206c79dd00aaa5f3f97","tid":473331,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bdbea91eb37e37d92004b6427ec3de1469ed8ae","tid":473331,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"有錢人既分別就係 佢可以選擇唔捱"},{"pid":"45d46e14bfb9190e25f00fbff90f9bdff0cffacd","tid":473331,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"係你未夠有錢"},{"pid":"8ff1ee531a2dff67799ef4a306a43d1a8074a001","tid":473331,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb4911009a635e785c7b5f4c2bfe8e9cdb5a7c8","tid":473331,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"有錢人都會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f51828564cb9cad32c843133478e5b2e11d4ca","tid":473331,"uid":107436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢人都會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家有技術移植個頭，死唔去，最多植物人<img src=\